name: Standard Edition Dawn of Dracula Blu-Ray
description:
This is a Pre-order Item! It will ship out the first week of January!!
(Prototype cover shown -  not final art)

DAWN OF DRACULA BLURAY (Standard Edition) - contains the complete movie in stunning 1080P HiDef with an upgraded Dolby Digital soundmix, but wait!  there's more !

* Alternate audio commentary track exclusive to the BluRay version featuring director Blake Powell and stars Marlena Midnite and Robyn Graves recorded 3 days after the first theatrical showing

*Collection of outtakes , bloopers and behind the scenes footage.

*Theatrical Trailer version 1

*Theatrical Trailer version 2

name: DAWN OF DRACULA MEGA SET!!
description:
This is the BEAST folks!

The Mega Set includes a limited to 500 DVD edition film can the is completely hand crafted, hand assembled, and hand numbered.

In addition to the film can DVD, this set includes a full size lobby card set!

Also a full sized, full color, 27" x 39" Dawn of Dracula theatrical lobby poster

AAAAAAAAND....

 limited to this set only: 11" x 17" spanish version poster!

Be sure to snag yours today as the Mega Set is limited to 100, and they are selling fast!!

Please keep in mind that DVDs will ship separately in a bubble mailer, while the paper good (posters and lobby cards will be shipped in a mailer tube so they are not folded or ruined during shipping!) We are sorry for this inconvenience, but it is for the good of your precious posters!

Paper goods will start shipping around the beginning of November.

name: Limited Edition Dawn of Dracula 2 Disc DVD Film Can Set!
description:
Here we have a special 2 disc limited edition of DAWN OF DRACULA in special filmcan packaging. Strictly limited to 500 numbered copies, it will include:
Dawn of Dracula feature length film on DVD including the complete movie, commentary track and a collection of outtakes and alternate scenes.

Dawn of Dracula soundtrack CD - contains the musical score by Thomas Berdinski as well as other original music used in the film (including The Fascist Tea Party's infamous single!!)

Mini Lobby Card Set- this limited edition release also contains miniature reproductions of the DAWN OF DRACULA lobbycards.

All of which are housed in a genuine 16mm - 200' film can!

Only 500 of this special filmcan DVD release will be made, so be sure to snap one up while you can!

These will begin shipping out around October 17th.

name: Dawn of Dracula Lobby Card Set
description:
A limited set of 6 genuine 11" x 14" DAWN OF DRACULA lobby cards printed on high quality matte card stock.

These will be limited to 250 sets, so get you hands on them while you can!

They will shipped to you safely rolled in a cardboard poster tube, if you like you can use it as a pirate telescope after you get your lobby cards out, or you can reuse it to keep other papery goods rolled up safe and sound.

These will begin shipping out October 17th

name: Midnite Mausoleum- DVD Set Season 1
description:
The first of the MIDNITE MAUSOLEUM™ multi DVD season collections!

Back from the dead are the first 12 web episodes of MIDNITE MAUSOLEUM™ from 2009. These 12 episodes have never been shown on television and are from the early formative stages of MIDNITE MAUSOLEUM™. Join Marlena and her friends as they bring Your weekly dose of Horror and Sci Fi cinema and it is all here for You, in 1 package! Each disc contains 4 complete episodes exactly as they were shown on the web in 2009 (sans the 3 extra repeated title sequences). PLUS they have a collection of outtakes PLUS they have an alternate audio commentary track by star Marlena Midnite, Andrew "Bones" Smith and Director Blake Powell.

name: Midnite Mausoleum- DVD EuroSleaze V1
description:
Not for the kiddo's folks! 
EuroSleaze edition DVD's are everything you COULDN'T see on TV!
Marlena, Robyn and the rest of the gang spice it up in this DVD only release, featuring: boobs, gore, succubi and a whole lot more! Also featuring a short by Thomas Berdinski (of Italian Zombie Movie fame) called "The Puppubus!" and I assure you it's AWESOME!

The movie featured on this DVD is "Devils Nightmare".
